name: Spaaace Cleaner
description: It can get the grime off of anything. Strips away the paint and effects from a tool. Ready for a new coat!

name: Red Paint
description: It's paint. It makes things red, like a barn door.

name: Blue Paint
description: It's paint. It makes things blue, like a deep ocean.

name: Yellow Paint
description: It's paint. It makes things yellow, like bright sunflowers.

name: Green Paint
description: It's paint. It makes things green, like fresh cut grass.

name: Purple Paint
description: It's paint. It makes things purple, like an extraordinary sunset.

name: Orange Paint
description: It's paint. It makes things orange, like a warm fire.

name: Black Paint
description: Swirling darkness, as black as your heart.

name: Paint Randomizer
description: Feeling fickle? Splash some of this on a tool! Can overwrite existing paint.

name: Invisibility Paint
description: Okay, so I know you're trying to eat ice cream without anyone noticing, but you're definitely going to lose any tool you paint with this.

name: Mr. Key
description: What's inside that box? It's a mystery only Mr. Key can answer.

name: Baby Key
description: Smol and squish. Needs to grow up to be useful.

name: Growth Juice
description: Drink up!

name: Old Shoebox
description: Contains an old item, maybe of marginal usefulness.

name: Chopsticks Case
description: Guess what? There are chopsticks in here.

name: Silverware Drawer
description: Maybe you'll get a spoon.
Contains something weird.

name: Banana?
description: Banana.

name: Wrapped Straw
description: Contains something that sucks. The wrapper is oddly strong.

name: Toybox
description: Open for silly toy. Play like a child.

name: Dart Gun Crate
description: This is a no violence zone, unless you're committing violence against your GUT when you eat ICE CREAM. Open for a toy pew-pew.

name: Golden Chest
description: SUPER SPECIAL MAGIC GOLDEN CHEST, in Mint condition. You definitely want to get whatever's inside.

name: Rainbow Sprinkles
description: A classic. (Single-use)

name: Chocolate Sprinkles
description: Boring but tasty. (Single-use)

name: Patriotic Sprinkles
description: What are we celebrating? (Single-use)

name: Halloween Sprinkles
description: Best holiday, best sprinkles. (Single-use)

name: Magic Sprinkles
description: Glowy, floaty, and arcane, what could go wrong? (Single-use)

name: Hot Fudge?
description: Uhhhh are you sure that's fudge? (Single-use)

name: Whipped Cream
description: More cream for your cream. (Single-use)

name: Whipped Cream with a Cherry on top
description: The pinnacle topping. (Single-use)

name: UFO
description: A stranger from a strange land. Jealous of your ice cream. (Single-use)

name: Chopsticks
description: When you don't have anything else to eat ice cream with, I suppose they'll have to do.

name: Chopsticks (tiny)
description: For tiny people eating tiny food.

name: Super Chopsticks
description: NEEDED: PROFESSIONAL CHOPSTICKS USER FOR ICE CREAM EATING

name: Inlaid Chopsticks
description: Chopsticks, but with a nice inlay.

name: Plastic Fork
description: From your last takeaway. Not dishwasher safe.

name: Tuning Fork
description: Its resonance is better for making music than eating ice cream.

name: Poseidon's Trident
description: Water Fork.

name: Butter Knife
description: Can only cut things that probably don't need to be cut.

name: Machete
description: Watch out! That ice cream might secretly be a zombie in disguise!

name: Broken Spoon
description: It's missing the useful part.

name: Ridiculously Long Spoon
description: I'm not sure where you're supposed to hold this when in polite society.

name: Magic Spoon
description: Enchanted with ice cream repellant.

name: Double Spoon
description: A weapon from a less civilized age.

name: Normal Spoon
description: A rare treasure!

name: Banana
description: See scale.

name: Moldy Banana
description: You probably shouldn't eat that.

name: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Banana
description: Save a horse, ride a banana.

name: Bluespace Banana
description: Researchers are mystified as to how and why bananas learned to teleport.

name: Cardboard Straw
description: It barely works and disintegrates into your drink when you use it. You live in the future!

name: Bendy Straw
description: The coolest kid in school always had a bendy straw in their drink.

name: Vacuum Cleaner
description: It sucks things up.

name: Boba Straw
description: The primo straw for when you wanna really suck things up.

name: Remote-Controlled Car
description: It's got the zoomies, but not a lot of battery.

name: Bug Net
description: I hope there are no bugs in your ice cream. Why do you need this?

name: Umbrella
description: Pops open and keeps you dry when it rains ice cream.

name: Spinner
description: Spin to win.

name: Shark Grabber
description: A bit bitey for my taste.

name: Dart Sniper
description: Single-shot foam dart gun. Not terribly accurate, but then again you've chosen to shoot ice cream rather than eat it like a normal person.

name: Dart Blaster
description: Holds a few foam darts, but has huge recoil.

name: Dart Sprayer
description: Shoots many foam darts very quickly. Chaos incarnate.

name: Cursed Chalice
description: You've gone too far now. You can never get rid of this.

name: Blender
description: Some people make spinach-ginger-cucumber shots in theirs, but this one specializes in grinding up boxes into consumables.

name: Gnome Shopkeeper
description: Where'd he come from?? He sells paint.

name: Personal Chopsticks
description: These belong to you.

name: White Paint
description: Bright white and freshly sanitized. Must be what hospitals use.

name: Gacha of Gacha
description: This box contains another box. You're welcome.

name: Ghost Chopsticks
description: Ethereal chopsticks. Single-use, can't be painted.

name: Ghost Spoon
description: Ethereal spoon. Single-use, can't be painted.

name: Ghost Straw
description: Ethereal straw. Single-use, can't be painted.

name: Beta Blue Paint
description: Special super blue paint, for early players.

name: Blue-Inlaid Chopsticks
description: Special inlaid chopsticks, for early players.

name: Dry Ice
description: Keeps nearby ice cream from melting. Do not eat! (Single-use)
